行
Fine.

1173
01:06:14,460 --> 01:06:15,970
你竟然还能找到咖啡
I can't believe you found coffee.

1174
01:06:18,450 --> 01:06:19,190
谢谢
Thank you.

1175
01:06:23,010 --> 01:06:24,010
加糖  对吗
Sugar, right?

1176
01:06:24,380 --> 01:06:25,130
是的
Yeah.

1177
01:06:31,210 --> 01:06:31,710
谢谢
Thank you.

1178
01:06:31,710 --> 01:06:34,230
等等  三包  你喜欢加三包
Ah, hold on. Three. You like three.

1179
01:06:47,980 --> 01:06:50,200
