How many times have we been here?

1181
01:07:07,130 --> 01:07:08,230
几次了
How many times?

1182
01:07:09,510 --> 01:07:10,640
钥匙在哪里
Where are the keys?

1183
01:07:12,190 --> 01:07:13,770
-那该死的钥匙在哪  -好吧
- Where are the goddamn keys? - Yeah, okay.

1184
