你会开飞机  是吗
You can fly it, can't you?

1185
01:07:18,790 --> 01:07:20,130
不会  好吧  
No. Well, yes.

1186
01:07:20,130 --> 01:07:21,560
是  我是说  我能起飞
I mean, I can take off.

1187
01:07:21,560 --> 01:07:23,100
还不会降落  所以
I'm still working on my landing, so...

1188
01:07:23,100 --> 01:07:24,300
那我们还在这里干什么
What are we still doing here?

1189
01:07:24,300 --> 01:07:25,470
你在浪费时间
You're wasting time!

1190
01:07:25,470 --> 01:07:27,670
丽塔  如果启动飞机你就会死
Rita, if you start that engine you die.

1191
