你都会死在这里
This is as far as you ever make it.

1194
01:07:46,270 --> 01:07:49,090
有一个变种在距离20码的地方埋伏着
There's a mimic buried twenty yards away.

1195
01:07:49,580 --> 01:07:51,460
你一启动引擎它就开始攻击
It attacks when you start the engine.

1196
01:07:52,980 --> 01:07:55,400
带上弹药上飞机  凯奇
Get your weapon and get in the helicopter, Cage.

1197
01:07:55,630 --> 01:07:57,350
田地里还有更多
There's more in the field back there.

1198
01:08:00,110 --> 01:08:01,540
我们俩只能活一个
Only one of us ever makes it.

1199
01:08:01,540 --> 01:08:02,200
上飞机
Get in.

1200
01:08:02,200 --> 01:08:03,460
我们唯一没有试过的方法就是
The only thing we haven't tried is the version

1201
01:08:03,460 --> 01:08:05,190
你离开这里  回到农舍
where you walk away. Just go back to the farmhouse.

1202
01:08:05,190 --> 01:08:06,720
那里有一个地窖  那儿有食物
There's a cellar. There's food.

1203
01:08:06,720 --> 01:08:08,460
你在那等我回来
You wait there till I get back.

1204
01:08:08,610 --> 01:08:09,780
你会很安全
You'll be safe.

1205
01:08:09,790 --> 01:08:12,110
我是一个战士  我心甘情愿
I'm a soldier. I volunteered.

1206
01:08:12,110 --> 01:08:13,020
我不会逃避
I'm not walking away.

1207
01:08:13,030 --> 01:08:14,230
你会死在这
You die here.

1208
01:08:14,660 --> 01:08:15,550
就在这
Right here.

1209
01:08:16,450 --> 01:08:19,100
我救不了你
I...can't save you.

1210
01:08:19,670 --> 01:08:22,950
如果我去杀欧米加  你会死
And if I go on and kill the omega, you're dead.

1211
01:08:23,610 --> 01:08:24,420
永远
Forever.

1212
01:08:24,690 --> 01:08:26,600
我出事了又有什么关系
Why does it matter what happens to me?

1213
01:08:30,640 --> 01:08:31,360
我希望
I wish...

1214
01:08:32,550 --> 01:08:33,560
我不认识你
I didn't know you...

1215
01:08:36,110 --> 01:08:36,980
但事实不是这样
But I do.

1216
01:10:08,610 --> 01:10:10,080
我的中间名
My middle name...

1217
01:10:11,460 --> 01:10:12,800
是萝丝
is rose.

1218
01:10:32,970 --> 01:10:34,570
站起来  你这废物
On your feet, maggot!

1219
01:10:46,010 --> 01:10:48,000
你还是有希望的  二等兵
The good news is there's hope for you, private.

1220
01:10:48,170 --> 01:10:50,410
参与光荣的战斗
Hope in the form of glorious combat.

1221
01:10:51,280 --> 01:10:53,010
战斗是最伟大的救赎
Battle is the great redeemer,

1222
01:10:53,020 --> 01:10:56,360
是锤炼真英雄的浴火熔炉
the fiery crucible in which the only true heroes are forged.

1223
01:10:56,870 --> 01:10:58,680
唯一一个众生...
The one place where all men...

1224
01:11:08,130 --> 01:11:08,870
有事吗
Yes?

1225
01:11:10,290 --> 01:11:11,830
谁允许你进来的
Who said you could talk to me?

1226
01:11:15,760 --> 01:11:17,620
我脸上有东西吗  大兵
Have I got something on my face, soldier?

1227
01:11:21,450 --> 01:11:22,800
不好意思打扰了  中士
I'm sorry to disturb you, sergeant.

1228
01:11:45,370 --> 01:11:46,740
好了  伙计  准备上战场
All right, man, let's get this show on the road.

1229
01:11:46,740 --> 01:11:47,890
我也得重装上阵了
I gotta suit up.

1230
01:11:48,240 --> 01:11:49,710
快点  基梅尔  开始了
Come on, Kimmel, let's have it!

1231
01:11:50,770 --> 01:11:51,690
你的头盔呢
Where's your helmet?

1232
01:11:53,640 --> 01:11:54,680
我从来不戴
Never wear one.

1233
01:11:55,400 --> 01:11:56,580
是个累赘
It's a distraction.

1234
01:11:59,280 --> 01:12:00,250
你喝醉了吗
Have you been drinking?

1235
01:12:00,250 --> 01:12:02,500
再给我三个五五六的弹簧夹
I need three more clips of five-five-six,

1236
01:12:02,790 --> 01:12:05,440
八个手雷  和一个备用电池
eight grenades and an extra battery.

1237
01:12:09,540 --> 01:12:10,280
快去拿
Get it.

1238
01:12:18,770 --> 01:12:20,150
伙计
Ey! Oi, mate!

1239
01:12:20,480 --> 01:12:22,280
你的战甲好像有点问题
I think there's something wrong with your suit.

1240
01:12:23,740 --> 01:12:25,270
有个死人在里面
There's a dead guy in it.

1241
01:12:26,330 --> 01:12:28,650
天啊  我们成功了
Woo-hoo! We made it!

1242
01:12:28,790 --> 01:12:30,180
感谢老天  我们成功了
Thank god, we made it!

1243
01:14:33,230 --> 01:14:33,960
干掉他
Finish it!

1244
01:15:29,510 --> 01:15:30,400
它不在那
It isn't there.

1245
01:15:30,530 --> 01:15:31,970
什么意思  欧米加不在那
What do you mean the omega isn't there?

1246
01:15:31,970 --> 01:15:34,930
我猜它们不在那  它们知道我们会去
My guess is it never was. They knew we were coming.

1247
01:15:34,930 --> 01:15:35,850
它们在那里埋伏我们
They ambushed us.

1248
01:15:35,850 --> 01:15:37,250
幻想是一个陷阱
The visions were a trap.

1249
01:15:39,150 --> 01:15:41,410
就像丽塔在凡尔登的幻想一样
Just like Rita's visions were a trap at Verdun.

1250
01:15:42,950 --> 01:15:44,430
它本可以杀了我它但没有
It could have killed me but it didn't.

1251
01:15:44,880 --> 01:15:45,920
它们只是要我的血
It's after my blood.

1252
01:15:45,920 --> 01:15:46,900
所以他们知道你是谁
So they know who you are.

1253
01:15:46,900 --> 01:15:50,280
他们想恢复自己的能量
They... they want their power back.

1254
01:15:50,290 --> 01:15:51,940
他们迟早会得逞的
And they're gonna get it one way or another.

1255
01:15:51,940 --> 01:15:53,850
除非我们找到欧米加
Unless we find the omega.

1256
01:15:53,850 --> 01:15:56,180
没别的办法了  我们完了
The... there isn't any other way. We're finished.

1257
01:15:56,180 --> 01:15:58,270
不  还没完
No. We're not finished.

1258
01:15:58,470 --> 01:15:59,800
那个没有用  我无法让它工作
That doesn't work. I-I can't get it to work.

1259
01:15:59,800 --> 01:16:01,120
你在怀特霍尔造了一个原型
You built a prototype at Whitehall...

1260
01:16:01,120 --> 01:16:03,770
是的  还害我丢了工作  托你的福
yes, and I got fired for it, thank you very much.

1261
01:16:04,190 --> 01:16:05,140
话说回来  那到底是什么
Wh-what is this thing, anyway?

1262
01:16:05,140 --> 01:16:06,090
是一个转发器
It's a transponder.

1263
01:16:06,090 --> 01:16:07,140
把它插入阿尔法体内
You stick it into the Alpha,

1264
01:16:07,140 --> 01:16:09,500
它会用波长信息连接欧米加
and it taps into the wavelength connecting it to the omega.

1265
01:16:09,500 --> 01:16:11,350
这就是原理
That's the idea, anyway.

1266
01:16:11,630 --> 01:16:12,890
但是我无法让它工作
But I can't get it to work.

1267
01:16:12,890 --> 01:16:14,720
现在手头的设备根本不行
Not with the equipment I have on hand.

1268
01:16:17,120 --> 01:16:18,500
怎样才能弄到你想要的东西
How do we get you what you need?

1269
01:16:18,500 --> 01:16:19,240
好吧  这就是问题所在
Well, that's the thing.

1270
01:16:19,240 --> 01:16:21,440
我在怀特霍尔造了一个
I mean, when I was at Whitehall I built one.

1271
01:16:21,440 --> 01:16:22,730
都已经到测试阶段了
I was even ready to test it.

1272
01:16:22,730 --> 01:16:24,440
当我跟上级反应的时候
When I told my superiors about it...

1273
01:16:24,640 --> 01:16:25,600
我就丢了工作
Well, I lost my job.

1274
01:16:25,600 --> 01:16:26,880
他们都觉得他疯了
They thought he was crazy.

1275
01:16:27,590 --> 01:16:29,220
所以我们只要去怀特霍尔
So all we need to do is go to Whitehall.

1276
01:16:29,850 --> 01:16:32,180
还没接近大门你就会被逮捕
You'd be arrested ten feet from the front door.

1277
01:16:32,180 --> 01:16:33,830
精神病院  解剖  记得吗
Psych ward. Dissection. Remember?

1278
01:16:33,830 --> 01:16:36,340
嘿  难道你忘了吗
Hey, hey, hey! Aren't you forgetting something?

1279
01:16:36,450 --> 01:16:39,210
转换器需要一个活体阿尔法才能工作
The transponder requires a live Alpha to make it work.

1280
01:16:39,210 --> 01:16:42,760
我们不需要  我们有更好的
We don't need one. We got the next best thing.

1281
01:16:46,300 --> 01:16:48,020
中国代表团出来的时候
When the Chinese delegation comes out...

1282
01:16:48,020 --> 01:16:49,350
我们加快脚步
We pick up the pace.

1283
01:16:51,480 --> 01:16:53,920
带黄袖章的人总能把你认出来
This guy with the yellow armband always recognizes you...

1284
01:16:53,930 --> 01:16:57,130
把头低下  站在我的右边
So just keep your head down and stay to my right.

1285
01:17:04,080 --> 01:17:05,100
干得好
Nicely done.

1286
01:17:08,250 --> 01:17:10,120
三  二  一
Three, two, one.

1287
01:17:10,120 --> 01:17:10,860
走
Go.

1288
01:17:10,950 --> 01:17:11,680
一
One...

1289
01:17:14,700 --> 01:17:16,100
六  七
Six, seven...

1290
01:17:16,170 --> 01:17:16,920
八
Eight...

1291
01:17:24,030 --> 01:17:25,950
转身
And, turn.

1292
01:17:26,930 --> 01:17:29,280
好  继续走  盯着前面
Okay. Keep walking. Just stare straight ahead.

1293
01:17:30,850 --> 01:17:31,600
罗宾逊
Robinson.

1294
01:17:32,730 --> 01:17:34,320
我说了别打扰我
I've asked not to be disturbed.

1295
01:17:34,320 --> 01:17:35,570
最好是特别紧急的事情
This had better be critical.

1296
01:17:35,570 --> 01:17:36,870
人类的命运
The fate of mankind.

1297
01:17:37,070 --> 01:17:38,100
够紧急吗
Critical enough?

1298
01:17:39,020 --> 01:17:40,320
真不敢我的眼睛
I don't believe what I'm seeing.

1299
01:17:40,470 --> 01:17:42,290
我也见多不怪了
I've had more than my share of that.

1300
01:17:42,660 --> 01:17:45,100
坐下  将军  离那张桌子远一点
Sit down, general. Stay away from the desk.

1301
01:17:45,780 --> 01:17:47,820
如果我是你  就会听她的话
I'd take her very seriously if I were you.

1302
01:17:49,870 --> 01:17:51,300
不得不佩服你  少将
Have to hand it to you, major.

1303
01:17:52,350 --> 01:17:53,480
今天你离开办公室的时候
When you left this office today,

1304
01:17:53,480 --> 01:17:55,050
我从未想过你会再回来
I never imagined you'd be back,

1305
01:17:55,050 --> 01:17:57,250
更别说还跟我授奖最多的战士一起
let alone with my most decorated soldier.

1306
01:17:57,280 --> 01:17:58,460
我要给你讲个故事  将军
I'm gonna tell you a story, general.

1307
01:17:58,460 --> 01:18:00,020
一开始听起来有些荒谬
And, at first, it's gonna sound ridiculous,

1308
01:18:00,020 --> 01:18:03,240
但越到后面  越会显得合理
but the longer I talk, the more rational it's going to appear.

1309
01:18:03,240 --> 01:18:04,460
跟他说过会儿打给他
Tell him you'll call back.

1310
01:18:04,930 --> 01:18:05,570
告诉谁
Tell who?

1311
01:18:05,570 --> 01:18:07,510
博蒙特少将  从哈利法克斯打来的
Major general Beaumont, calling from Halifax.

1312
01:18:07,520 --> 01:18:09,760
他的航班因为天气原因延误了
His plane has just been delayed. Bad weather.

1313
01:18:10,460 --> 01:18:11,200
是
Yes.

1314
01:18:14,710 --> 01:18:16,450
谢谢  博蒙特  待会儿打给你
Thank you, Beaumont. I'll call you back.

1315
01:18:19,170 --> 01:18:20,620
明天的侵袭将会是一场大屠杀
Tomorrow's invasion is a slaughter.

1316
01:18:20,620 --> 01:18:22,550
登滩不过五分钟我就会死
I'm dead within five minutes of landing on that beach,

1317
01:18:22,550 --> 01:18:24,870
和那些你派出去的所有士兵一起
along with every other soldier you are sending.

1318
01:18:24,870 --> 01:18:27,450
因为敌人早知道我们的计划
And that's because the enemy knows we're coming.

1319
01:18:27,600 --> 01:18:29,630
我怎么会知道  我临死前
How do I know this? Before I died,

1320
01:18:29,630 --> 01:18:31,860
杀死了一只变种  不过这只有些不寻常
i killed a mimic, only this one was different.

1321
01:18:31,860 --> 01:18:34,050
