It passed something on to me. In my blood.

1322
01:18:34,050 --> 01:18:36,820
现在我不停地重复同一天的生活
Now I live the same day over and over again.

1323
01:18:36,820 --> 01:18:38,070
就和他们一样
Just like they do.

1324
01:18:38,070 --> 01:18:39,460
就像薇拉塔斯基军士
Just like sergeant Vrataski...

1325
01:18:39,460 --> 01:18:40,580
在凡尔登的时候一样
At Verdun.

1326
01:18:40,890 --> 01:18:42,930
告诉你的秘书一切正常
Tell your secretary everything's fine.

1327
01:18:43,770 --> 01:18:44,660
