Beg your pardon?

1328
01:18:47,990 --> 01:18:50,480
对不起  上校  我以为只有你一个人
Um, I'm...sorry, general. I thought you were alone.

1329
01:18:50,480 --> 01:18:51,400
没关系
It's fine.

1330
01:18:51,700 --> 01:18:53,660
她打印了一些命令  等你签字
She typed up those orders for you to authorize.

1331
01:18:53,660 --> 01:18:55,540
但是她忘了关于格林威治
But she left out the ones referring to the fuel dump

1332
01:18:55,540 --> 01:18:56,610
燃油卸除的部分
at Greenwich.

1333
01:18:58,960 --> 01:19:00,050
你叫爱丽斯
Your name is Iris.

1334
01:19:00,050 --> 01:19:02,050
九月十七日出生
Your birthday is September seventeenth.

1335
01:19:02,440 --> 01:19:04,140
