The general quietly pulled some strings,

1336
01:19:04,140 --> 01:19:05,740
把你唯一的儿子安排在澳大利亚
stationed your only son in Australia,

1337
01:19:05,740 --> 01:19:07,480
尽可能的远离这场战争
as far from the war as possible.

1338
01:19:07,790 --> 01:19:09,370
告诉上校他的晚餐取消了
Tell the general his dinner's just been canceled.

1339
01:19:09,370 --> 01:19:10,740
是刚刚接到命令
The call came in just now.

1340
01:19:12,940 --> 01:19:14,480
你的晚餐已经被取消了
Your dinner was canceled.

1341
01:19:14,940 --> 01:19:16,400
你忘记了燃料卸除的部分
You forgot the fuel dump.

1342
01:19:17,680 --> 01:19:19,320
谢谢  爱丽斯  你可以出去了
Thank you, Iris. That'll be all.

1343
01:19:27,470 --> 01:19:28,850
